## Improvements
Feel free to enhance your `call_llm` function as needed. Here are examples:

- Handle chat history:

```python
def call_llm(messages):
    from openai import OpenAI
    client = OpenAI(api_key="YOUR_API_KEY_HERE")
    r = client.chat.completions.create(
        model="gpt-4o",
