       revision_count < 5: increment and return "revise"; if >= 5: return
       "max_revisions"; else "pass". Stream â€œStyle check k/5: â€¦â€.

9. EditCycleReportNode
   - Purpose: On 5th failure, produce a concise user-facing report; proceed.
   - Type: Regular
   - Steps:
